did.unittitle: Paul E. Sluby Cemetery Research Collection

custodhist.head: Custodial History
custodhist.p: Paul E. Sluby, Sr. donated his cemetery research files to the DC Community Archives in 2012.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection consists of newspaper clippings, emails, and Sluby's notes on various cemeteries in Washington, DC. Files are arranged alphabetically by cemetery name, followed by cemetery-related topics.
